<h2>5. Security & Access Control</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Test Case ID</th>
    <th>Test Scenario</th>
    <th>Steps to Execute</th>
    <th>Expected Result</th>
    <th>Status</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>TC-SEC-01</td>
    <td>Protected Routes</td>
    <td>1. Log out.<br>2. Attempt to manually navigate to /dashboard via URL.</td>
    <td>The application immediately redirects the user to /login.</td>
    <td class="pass">PASS</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>TC-SEC-02</td>
    <td>Data Isolation</td>
    <td>1. Create User A and upload a file.<br>2. Log out and log in as User B.</td>
    <td>User B's dashboard is empty. User B cannot see or access User A's uploaded files.</td>
    <td class="pass">PASS</td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
